{"type": "article", "id": 18143, "title": "分层陶瓷水杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-27T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000411jLlT4IsQ9r5XfuYa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个水杯是包装设计网站 Dieline 邀请陶艺家 Ben Medansky 等人设计的，它的材料来源于美国西南部，购买则可以为美国最大的印第安部落的纳瓦霍人带去自来水。水杯表面呈现出岩石一样的分层，从土壤到水再到天空，颜色很干净，可以用来做花瓶。每个杯子都有独特的编号，售价 138 美元，<a href=\"http://www.navajowaterproject.org/shop\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000409Vgi4HxOW0TF1DANZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000409Bvk97x4TqQFJzDsY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000410pg0tSA5McGFWfbEz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060600041040kQ1KpohNxfTya6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}